    "body": "My bad, I was the one introducing `dedupe` and I did not add any tests to it.\n\nI agree we need to have tests to prove that we actually fixed a bug and prevent future regressions. But adding the same tests to all widgets is cumbersome. Does it mean we'll have to add this boilerplate test to all new widgets?\n\nI have no answer to that unfortunatly.\n",
